      "content": "i see. so some people would say that the UN is basically just a tool for the big powers to do what they want anyway? if the structure depends on the countries involved and they just use it when it suits them, doesn't that make the whole idea of \"international law\" or \"global security\" through the UN kind of a myth? or is there a real way it actually holds power?",
